# SES Escalation Overhaul — Implementation Issues

**Goal:** Replace per-tile tracking/notification with a unified, manager-centric escalation workflow across all audit engines.

**Strategy:** 5 sequential issues. Each is a full deliverable. Do not start issue N+1 until N is merged.

**Total estimated effort:** ~3–4 weeks for one engineer, ~2 weeks for a pair.

---

## Dependency graph

```
Issue 1 (Directory)  ─┐
                      ├──▶ Issue 3 (Escalation Center UI) ──▶ Issue 4 (Composer) ──▶ Issue 5 (Automation)
Issue 2 (Data Model) ─┘
```

Issue 1 and Issue 2 can run in parallel. Everything else is strictly sequential.

