## Rollout & migration notes

**Feature flags.** Ship each issue behind a flag. Enable per-tenant for early feedback before global rollout. Particularly important for Issue 3 (breaking UX change).

**Data migration.** Issue 2 backfills `projectStatuses` and `stage`. Run in staging first; verify row counts match pre-migration.

**Training.** Issue 3 ships with an in-app product tour (first-time Escalation Center visit). One screen, 4 highlights: manager table, engine pills, slide-over panel, banner on process dashboard.

**Rollback plan.** Issues 1, 2, 4, 5 are additive — safe to disable via flag. Issue 3 removes TrackingTab; keep it feature-flagged for one release so rollback is flag-flip, not code-revert.

**Docs to update.** Admin guide (Issue 1 directory, Issue 4 templates), user guide (Issue 3 new workflow, Issue 5 shortcuts), API docs (all new endpoints).